---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Home" description="Real & Raw Gospel - Training the Remnant. Walk in the Spirit, learn the Feasts of YAH, engage in spiritual warfare, and discover your identity in Mashiach.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-950 via-neutral-900 to-black border-b border-neutral-800 text-white py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-amber-100">Real & Raw Gospel</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-4 text-amber-200">Training the Remnant in the Ways of YAHUAH</p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        No fluff. No compromise. Pure truth from the Word of YAHUAH. Walk in the RUACH HAQODESH, 
        honor the Feasts, and prepare for the return of YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/start-here" class="inline-block bg-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black transition-colors">
          Start Here
        </a>
        <a href="/bible" class="inline-block bg-neutral-800 hover:bg-neutral-700 border border-neutral-700 text-amber-100 font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black transition-colors">
          Read the Bible
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-black">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-amber-100">Core Training Paths</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <a href="/start-here" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Start Here</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Begin your journey. Essential foundations for walking with YAHUAH.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/walk-in-the-spirit" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Walk in the Spirit</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Live by the RUACH HAQODESH. Daily consecration and obedience.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/prayer-and-fasting" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Prayer & Fasting</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Sharpen your spiritual weapons through prayer and fasting.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/feasts" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Feasts of YAH</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Honor the appointed times. Learn the sacred calendar of YAHUAH.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/spiritual-warfare" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Spiritual Warfare</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Put on the armor of YAHUAH. Fight with spiritual authority.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/identity-and-messiah" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Identity & Mashiach</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Know who you are in YAHUSHA HAMASHIACH. Your true identity.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/end-times" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">End-Times</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Understand the season. Prepare for what's coming.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/videos" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Videos</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Watch powerful teachings and testimonies from the remnant.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/bible" class="group block p-6 bg-neutral-900 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-900/20 transition-all border border-neutral-800 hover:border-amber-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-amber-100 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">Bible Reader</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-400">Read Scripture with Sacred Names. Toggle between versions.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-neutral-950 border-t border-neutral-800 py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-amber-100">Ready to Begin?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        The hour is late. The remnant is being called. Will you answer?
      </p>
      <a href="/start-here" class="inline-block bg-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black transition-colors">
        Begin Your Training
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
